&lt;p&gt;Nice set of books. Pity I'm in the middle of &lt;em&gt;all of them&lt;/em&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Lately I have a hard time finishing many novels, I think because waiting
for the plot to play out gets boring. Although &lt;em&gt;River of Gods&lt;/em&gt; has mostly
