each box is a chapter, and that big box I'm just at the start of scares me:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://kitenet.net/~joey/blog/./pics/chapters.png&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://kitenet.net/~joey/blog/./pics/chapters.png&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; width=&quot;784&quot; height=&quot;21&quot; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Dishwasher is fun light reading. If I'd thought to bring it to its owner,
