involved, and rather out of my usual comfort zone.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Real World Haskell is coming along well, I hope.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Matter hasn't pulled me in yet, oddly.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Ars Magica I've been flipping through the PDF of idly.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;hr /&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Anyway, after all that, turning up a &lt;a href=&quot;http://grandtextauto.org/2008/11/30/three-1k-story-generators/&quot;&gt;random story generator in 1 kilobyte
of code&lt;/a&gt;
couldn't help but feel like a relief.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
